                     <interp inst="t18460921-1954-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 4 brushes, value 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 1 mane-comb, 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; and 1 curry-comb, 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18460921-name-1038" type="victimName">
